    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const roleType = $('Download Resume').item.json.Role_Type || \"\";\nconst cvText = $json.text || \"\";\n\nconst sweJD = {\n  \"role\": \"Software Engineer\",\n  \"experience\": \"2+ years professional development\",\n  \"education\": \"BS Computer Science or related\",\n  \"must_have\": [\n    \"Backend language: Python, Go, Java, or Node.js\",\n    \"REST API design and development\",\n    \"SQL or NoSQL database experience\",\n    \"Git version control\",\n    \"Production-level project experience\"\n  ],\n  \"good_to_have\": [\n    \"Cloud: AWS, GCP, or Azure\",\n    \"Docker or Kubernetes\",\n    \"CI/CD pipelines\",\n    \"System design knowledge\",\n    \"Open source contributions\"\n  ],\n  \"scoring\": {\n    \"80_100\": \"Strong: production systems, measurable impact, cloud/DevOps, 4+ years\",\n    \"50_79\": \"Average: real projects but limited scale, 2-3 years\",\n    \"0_49\": \"Weak: tutorials only, no production exp, vague skills\"\n  }\n};\n\nconst bdmJD = {\n  \"role\": \"Business Development Manager\",\n  \"experience\": \"3+ years B2B sales or BD\",\n  \"education\": \"BBA or MBA preferred\",\n  \"must_have\": [\n    \"Proven revenue generation with PKR/USD figures\",\n    \"Enterprise or SME client acquisition\",\n    \"CRM proficiency: Salesforce, HubSpot, or Zoho\",\n    \"Proposal writing and RFP experience\",\n    \"Pipeline management\"\n  ],\n  \"good_to_have\": [\n    \"GCC or international market exposure\",\n    \"Team leadership experience\",\n    \"Channel partner management\",\n    \"BD certifications\"\n  ],\n  \"scoring\": {\n    \"80_100\": \"Strong: clear revenue numbers, 3+ years, CRM tools, measurable wins\",\n    \"50_79\": \"Average: some sales exp, vague numbers, basic tools, potential shown\",\n    \"0_49\": \"Weak: no real BD exp, no metrics, retail or entry-level only\"\n  }\n};\n\nconst jd = roleType === \"Software Engineer\" ? sweJD : bdmJD;\n\nconst chatInput = `Role: ${roleType}\n\nJob Description:\n${JSON.stringify(jd, null, 2)}\n\nCV Content:\n${cvText}\n\nYou are an expert HR recruiter. Analyze the CV against the job description above and return ONLY a valid JSON object with no markdown, no code blocks, no extra text. Use exactly this structure:\n{\n  \"score\": <integer 0-100>,\n  \"classification\": \"<Strong|Average|Weak>\",\n  \"summary\": \"<2-3 sentence overview of the candidate>\",\n  \"strengths\": [\"<strength 1>\", \"<strength 2>\", \"<strength 3>\"],\n  \"concerns\": [\"<concern 1>\", \"<concern 2>\"],\n  \"interview_recommendation\": \"<Yes|No> - <one sentence reason>\"\n}`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    chatInput: chatInput\n  }\n}]; "
      },
